# perf_stress_capped.shot — M6 P03 heavy bench, "internal_h 1080" path.
#
# Mirror of perf_stress.shot with the internal cap on. The world +
# halftone+shimmer pass rasterise into 2580×1080 (2.79 Mpx); the
# upscale to the 3440×1440 backbuffer is a cheap bilinear blit.

window 3440 1440
seed   3 7
out    build/shots/perf_stress_capped
map    citadel
loadout Heavy "Mass Driver" "Frag Grenades" Heavy Burst

internal_h 1080
perf_overlay on

extra_chassis Heavy    1600 900
extra_chassis Scout    1900 900
extra_chassis Sniper   2200 900
extra_chassis Engineer 2500 900
extra_chassis Trooper  2800 900
extra_chassis Heavy    3100 900

aim 2000 900

at 30 press jet
at 580 release jet

at  60 shot t060
at 180 shot t180
at 300 shot t300
at 420 shot t420
at 540 shot t540
at 600 end
